Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/hellspite/dotfiles.git

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/dotfile/vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Switch to the `~/dotfiles` directory, and fetch submodules:

    cd ~/dotfiles
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
